lead_paragraph: Dutchman Robert Gesink won Stage 14 of the Tour of Spain on Saturday, finishing seven seconds ahead of the field as he returned to form after injury problems earlier in the year.

headline.print_headline: Cycling: Quintana and Froome Inseparable as Gesink Wins Stage
